orego.core

Class SuperKoTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • orego.core.SuperKoTable

  • public class SuperKoTable
extends Object
    Set of Zobrist hashes (longs) from previous board positions. This is a hash table, but without all of the overhead of java.util.HashSet. It only supports insertion, search, and copying. Collisions are resolved by linear probing.
